{
  "info": {
    "name": "OneInbox API v1",
    "description": "Voice AI platform API — composable resources (agents, LLM models, tools, webhooks, integrations, voices, knowledge bases, phone numbers, calls).\n\n## Setup\n1. `POST /v1/auth/signup` → JWT auto-saved to `{{jwt_token}}`\n2. `POST /v1/api-keys` → API key auto-saved to `{{api_key}}`\n3. Build resources in order: Integration → LLM Model → Webhook → Tool → KB → Voice → Agent → Call\n\n## Auth\n- **JWT** (`Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}`) — dashboard, Swagger docs, API key management\n- **API key** (`Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}`) — all resource endpoints\n\n## Variables\n- `base_url` — API server (default http://13.207.23.185:8000)\n- `jwt_token`, `api_key` — auto-set\n- `agent_id`, `call_id`, `phone_id`, `credential_id`, `tool_id`, `webhook_id`, `voice_id`, `kb_id`, `llm_id` — auto-set by create endpoints",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {"key": "base_url", "value": "http://13.207.23.185:8000"},
    {"key": "jwt_token", "value": ""},
    {"key": "api_key", "value": ""},
    {"key": "agent_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "call_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "phone_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "credential_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "tool_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "webhook_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "voice_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "kb_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "llm_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "twilio_auth_token", "value": "", "type": "secret"},
    {"key": "twilio_sip_password", "value": "", "type": "secret"}
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {"name": "Signup",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["if(pm.response.code===201){pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token',pm.response.json().access_token);}"]}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth/signup", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["v1","auth","signup"]},
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"founder@oneinbox.ai\",\n  \"password\": \"super-secret-123\",\n  \"name\": \"Founder\",\n  \"organization_name\": \"OneInbox\"\n}"}}},
        {"name": "Login",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["if(pm.response.code===200){pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token',pm.response.json().access_token);}"]}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["v1","auth","login"]},
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"founder@oneinbox.ai\",\n  \"password\": \"super-secret-123\"\n}"}}},
        {"name": "Logout",
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth/logout", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["v1","auth","logout"]}}},
        {"name": "Me",
          "request": {"method": "GET", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["v1","auth","me"]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "API Keys",
      "item": [
        {"name": "Create",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["if(pm.response.code===201){pm.collectionVariables.set('api_key',pm.response.json().api_key);}"]}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"},{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/api-keys", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["v1","api-keys"]},
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Production Key\"\n}"}}},
        {"name": "List",
